changelog.description:
**Added**


- **Multi-File Addons.** Meet Modules. These are unique addons that contain many files and have the same effects as plugins and themes! 
- **Crashed & Killed.** Alerts when something goes wrong internally. 
- **Typings.** Developers are at the top of our minds when developing Velocity, we now have in-depth API typings for you to use!  


**Changed**


- **Built-Ins.** Editor & Modal sizes. 
- **Updater.** Our new-and imporved updater lets you take more control over your Velocity installation!
changelog.subtitle: June 3, 2022
